<span class="usa-tag pmc-tag-pt">letter</span> <div class="display-inline-block"><button type="button" class="cursor-pointer text-no-underline bg-transparent border-0 padding-0 text-left margin-0 text-normal text-primary" aria-controls="journal_context_menu">Neuroophthalmology</button></div>. 2018 Jul 27;43(1):67–69. doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1080/01658107.2018.1465439" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10.1080/01658107.2018.1465439</a>
